  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Dealing with zero values"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "There are several scenarios we check here. The first is where the old balance and new balance of the destination = 0 even though the amount transacted is non zero. The second is where the old and new balance of the origin = 0 even though the amount transacted is non zero. \n",
    "The third is where the amount is 0 and the transaction is still labeled fraud."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Checking time of day"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We can also group the data by time of day. We define morning as hour 6-11, afternoon as 11-5, evening as 5-9, and night as 10-6.\n",
    "The step column is broken down into hours of the month, ranging from 1 to 744, for a total of 31 days. Note though that our reduced data has a max step of 718.\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 160,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# We assign the step values into a time of day to see if fraud is coorelated to time of day at all\n",
    "\n",
    "morning_transaction = []\n",
    "noon_transaction = []\n",
    "evening_transaction = []\n",
    "night_transaction = []\n",
    "\n",
    "time_slots = [range(6,12), range(11,18), range(17,22), range(21,30)]\n",
    "\n",
    "for t in time_slots:\n",
    "    for x in t:\n",
    "        for i in range(718):\n",
    "            transaction = (x + (24*i))\n",
    "            if transaction <= 718:\n",
    "                if t == time_slots[0]:\n",
    "                    morning_transaction.append(transaction)\n",
    "                if t == time_slots[1]:\n",
    "                    noon_transaction.append(transaction)\n",
    "                if t == time_slots[2]:\n",
    "                    evening_transaction.append(transaction)\n",
    "                if t == time_slots[3]:\n",
    "                    night_transaction.append(transaction)"
   ]
  },
